list.name: First commit
list.comment: Include all FSL file. connectopic_mapping.npy implements version 1 of haak paper.

changelist.name: First commit
changelist.comment: Include all FSL file. connectopic_mapping.npy implements version 1 of haak paper.

task.summary: Include Haak version of connectopic mapping as described in the relative paper.
Fixed input of fingerprint computation in Haak connectopic mapping such that voxels correlated in normal space are still correlated in SVD space.
Last commit before merging branch to master.
Changed manifold learning algorithm from spectral embedding to tSNE.
Fixed similarity->distance transformation. Changed manifold learning to 3 dimensions. Changed visualization color space to RGB, where each channel corresponds to a tSNE output dimension.
Removed GP optimization. Added option to don't save results.
Changed input and pushed before checking out manifold_v2 branch.
Modified code to work on 2 concatenated scans
Added parameter to choose manifold learning method.
Added "graph disconnect" to spectral manifold learning method.
